column4:
Thanks to 
@vandersluis11
 and 
@ktwu11
 for inviting me to discuss systemic racism and my administration's plans to make our state a more equitable home for all Kansans. Tune in at 7:30 p.m. Thursday, June 18.

Today I am also announcing that we will create a new Ohio Office of Law Enforcement Recruitment within 
@Ohio_OCJS
 to help local agencies with the recruitment and retention of minorities and women in law enforcement.

As we approach Peace Officers Memorial Day tomorrow, we remember Ohio's officers killed in the line of duty in 2019-20. 
 
Officer Dale Woods, 
@ColerainPolice
Det. William Brewer, 
@ClermontSheriff
Det. Jorge Del Rio, 
@DaytonPolice
 
Officer Kaia Grant, Springdale Police Dept.

At only 29 years of age, Officer Bohannon had already established himself as a model public servant and law enforcement officer. In just four years with 
@SLMPD
, he was honored twice with the Department’s Award of Excellence and twice as Officer of the Month.

The 
@MSHPTrooperGHQ
 will continue to support local law enforcement with law enforcement efforts. 

The 
@Missouri_NG
’s presence means more law enforcement officers are available to respond to protests and any potential criminal activity.

On Friday, 
@MoSEMA_
 distributed 17,800 goggles, more than 1,700 boxes of gloves, and over 75,000 bottles of hand sanitizer to local law enforcement and fire service agencies.

As 
@Chicago
 works to prevent more violence this weekend, Illinois State Police have worked hand-in-hand all week with CPD to assist. We are ready to help with any available state public safety resources.
